(179, 1, '2015-02-24 11:24:56', '2015-02-24 11:24:56', '<h3 class="lead">Bootstrap:  web Design Framwork</h3>\nBootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework for developing responsive, mobile first projects on the web. <a title="Bootstrap" href="http://getbootstrap.com/" target="_blank">Bootstrap</a> is an HTML5 &amp; CSS3 framework designed to help you kickstart the development of webapps and sites.\nmain site &amp; documentation: <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/">http://getbootstrap.com/</a>\n<h3>Wrap Bootstrap</h3>\nWrapBootstrap is a marketplace for premium Bootstrap themes and templates. Impress your clients and visitors while using a single, rock-solid foundation.\nLink : <a href="https://wrapbootstrap.com/">https://wrapbootstrap.com/</a>\n<h3>Bootswatch</h3>\noffers Free themes for Bootstrap : <a href="http://bootswatch.com/">http://bootswatch.com/</a>\n<h3>ZeroBootstrap</h3>\nThe largest open-source, free Bootstrap template collection. Link : <a href="http://bootstrapzero.com/">http://bootstrapzero.com/</a>\n<h3>startbootstrap</h3>\nFree Bootstrap Themes &amp; Templates. Link : <a href="http://startbootstrap.com/">http://startbootstrap.com/</a>\n<h3>BootBundle</h3>\nLink: <a href="http://www.bootbundle.com/tool">http://www.bootbundle.com/tool</a>\n<h3>Angularjs Bootstrap Directives</h3>\nLink: <a href="http://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/">http://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/</a>', 'Bootstrap 3 with some friends is here ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oh-my-god-bootstrap-3-is-here', '', '', '2015-02-24 14:29:18', '2015-02-24 14:29:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/blog2/?p=179', 0, 'post', '', 0),
