(200, 1, '2015-02-27 08:41:38', '2015-02-27 08:41:38', '<h3>Android Studio installation on Windows 7 fails, no JDK found --- Error</h3>\n<a href="http://localhost/blog2/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/android1.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-201" src="http://localhost/blog2/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/android1-300x169.jpg" alt="android1" width="985" height="555" /></a>\n<h3></h3>\n<ol>\n	<li>download jdk then install it</li>\n	<li>add the ??\java\jdk??\bin\ to your system variable paths</li>\n	<li>Add a system variable <code>JDK_HOME</code> with value <code>??\Java\jdk??\</code></li>\n	<li>works find.</li>\n</ol>\nMore info :<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16574189/android-studio-installation-on-windows-7-fails-no-jdk-found"> http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16574189/android-studio-installation-on-windows-7-fails-no-jdk-found</a>', 'Android Studio installation fails - no JDK found', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'android-studio-installation-on-windows-7-fails-no-jdk-found', '', '', '2015-02-27 08:46:01', '2015-02-27 08:46:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/blog2/?p=200', 0, 'post', '', 0),
