(236, 1, '2015-02-28 12:58:28', '2015-02-28 12:58:28', '<a href="http://localhost/blog2/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/android.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-209" src="http://localhost/blog2/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/android-300x180.jpg" alt="android" width="560" height="336" /></a>\nLink for google''s nine patch Project: <a href="http://romannurik.github.io/AndroidAssetStudio/nine-patches.html" target="_blank">http://romannurik.github.io/AndroidAssetStudio/nine-patches.html</a>\n\nLink to Learn what''s nine patch :<a href="http://developer.android.com/tools/help/draw9patch.html"> http://developer.android.com/tools/help/draw9patch.html</a>', 'Google''s (Nine-Patch project) an Image Generator for andriod', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'googles-nine-patch-project-an-image-generator-for-andriod', '', '', '2015-02-28 14:58:57', '2015-02-28 14:58:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/blog2/?p=236', 0, 'post', '', 0),
